mapCenter<-c((max(libTbl$WGS84)+min(libTbl$WGS84))/2, (max(libTbl$WGS84)+min(libTbl$WGS84))/2)

yonginMap<-get_map(mapCenter, zoom = 12, maptype = 'roadmap')
## Map from URL : http://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=37.284545,127.161957&zoom=12&size=640x640&scale=2&maptype=roadmap&language=en-EN&sensor=false
ggmap(yonginMap) + 
  geom_point(data=libTbl, aes(x=WGS84, y=WGS84), color= "red",
             size=(libTbl$+libTbl$+libTbl$)/50000) +
  geom_text(data=libTbl, aes(x=WGS84, y=WGS84+0.005, label=), color= "black", size=2)
